n> <span lang=\"KO\">증명합니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">건물의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">무게를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">줄이면서</span> <span lang=\"KO\">내구성을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">높이고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">에너지를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">절약하는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">등</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가장</span> <span lang=\"KO\">중요한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">것은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">환경을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">효과적으로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">보호하는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">데</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기여합니다</span>.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">위의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">이점으로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">건설중인</span> <span lang=\"KO\">친환경</span> <span lang=\"KO\">자재는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">항상</span> <span lang=\"KO\">정부의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">지원을 받습니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">그리고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">이것은 기업이 선택해야할 첫번쨰 프로젝트가 될</span> <span lang=\"KO\">것입니다</span>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'quang', 'Tuấn Anh', 18, 'blog', '2020-10-01 08:06:25', '2022-02-14 00:51:19');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`blog_id`, `blog_ten`, `blog_ten_en`, `blog_ten_vi`, `blog_ten_zh`, `blog_ten_ja`, `blog_ten_kr`, `blog_place`, `blog_place_en`, `blog_slug`, `blog_thumb`, `blog_noidung`, `blog_noidung_en`, `blog_noidung_vi`, `blog_noidung_zh`, `blog_noidung_ja`, `blog_noidung_kr`, `blog_noibat`, `blog_hienthi`, `blog_title`, `blog_mota`, `blog_mota_vi`, `blog_mota_en`, `blog_mota_zh`, `blog_mota_ja`, `blog_mota_kr`, `blog_keyword`, `blog_nguoiviet`, `blog_editor`, `blog_blogcatid`, `blog_type`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(74, NULL, 'Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment', 'Các công ty xây dựng Nhật Bản tìm kiếm cơ hội đầu tư ngoài nước', '日本建筑公司在寻找新的海外投资机会', '海外投資の新たな機会を模索する日本の建設会社', '해외 투자의 새로운 기회를 모색하는 일본 건설사', '', '', 'cac-cong-ty-xay-dung-nhat-ban-tim-kiem-co-hoi-dau-tu-ngoai-nuoc', '16018620453123_image001.jpg', NULL, '<div class=\"w795 left\">\r\n<article class=\"detail-article\">\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\"><strong>(Construction) - Japanese construction contractors are embarking on overseas businesses other than construction contracts.</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3123_image001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Windpower Firm by Toda Corporation</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It including real estate investment, large-scale development, and renewable energy with an aim to accumulate business know-how and diversify its portfolio. Haseko Corporation announced in August that it will participate in a 292-unit housing development project in suburban Los Angels, the United States. Construction will begin in 2022, with completion slated in 2024. The US subsidiary of Takamatsu Construction Group has established a joint venture with a local real estate company to develop apartment buildings in a resort area in California, where many luxury properties are located.</p>\r\n<p>Toda Corporation purchased an office building in Irvine, California, the first full-scale real estate investment in the country. Taisei Corporation acquired a majority of the rights to own two office buildings in Boston, Massachusetts, which has made the company&rsquo;s first US real estate investment in 20 years.</p>\r\n<table class=\"MASTERCMS_TPL_TABLE\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-style: hidden; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3124_image003.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Housing Project by Haseko</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>The growing Asian market is also a promising target for Japanese construction businesses. In Hai Phong, Vietnam, the large-scaled hotel development \"Waterfront City Project\" was completed in March by Daiwa House Industry and Fujita. The total 39,814 square meters hotel is aimed at Japanese business travelers and domestic and foreign tourists.</p>\r\n<p>Kumagai Gumi and Sumitomo Forestry launched a joint venture in Singapore to promote real estate development overseas. The 50,000 square-meter project of a high rise condominium and a commercial building to be developed in Jakarta, Indonesia is the first project of the company.</p>\r\n<p>Toda Corporation has set Brazil as one of its new targets. It launched a project to construct offshore wind power plant in the northeastern part of the country. The total power output is 27.7 MW and is scheduled to start operation in July 2021. The company hopes \"to expand to the real estate business in the future.\" (2020/9/09)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>The Daily Engineering and Construction News of Japan</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"img-random\" class=\"category tin-cu-hon\">\r\n<div class=\"scroller-status\">\r\n<p class=\"infinite-scroll-error\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\"><strong>(X&acirc;y dựng) - C&aacute;c nh&agrave; thầu x&acirc;y dựng Nhật Bản đang bắt tay v&agrave;o việc kinh doanh c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh kh&aacute;c ngo&agrave;i x&acirc;y dựng</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3123_image001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></strong></em></div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y điện gi&oacute; của Toda Corporation</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Đ&oacute; bao gồm đầu tư bất động sản, đầu tư ph&aacute;t triển quy m&ocirc; lớn v&agrave; năng lượng t&aacute;i tạo nhằm mục đ&iacute;ch t&iacute;ch lũy kinh nghiệm v&agrave; đa dạng h&oacute;a danh mục đầu tư. Haseko Corporation th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o sẽ tham gia v&agrave;o dự &aacute;n ph&aacute;t triển nh&agrave; ở quy m&ocirc; 292 căn ở ngoại &ocirc; Los Angeles. Việc x&acirc;y dựng sẽ bắt đầu v&agrave;o 2022, dự kiến kết th&uacute;c v&agrave;o 2024. C&ocirc;ng ty con của Tập đo&agrave;n X&acirc;y dựng Takamatsu của Mỹ đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh lập li&ecirc;n doanh với một c&ocirc;ng ty bất động sản địa phương để ph&aacute;t triển c&aacute;c t&ograve;a nh&agrave; căn hộ trong một khu nghỉ dưỡng ở California, nơi c&oacute; nhiều bất động sản cao cấp.</p>\r\n<p>Tập đo&agrave;n Toda đ&atilde; mua một t&ograve;a nh&agrave; văn ph&ograve;ng ở Irvine, California, đ&acirc;y l&agrave; khoản đầu tư bất động sản quy m&ocirc; lớn đầu ti&ecirc;n ở nước n&agrave;y. Taisei Corporation đ&atilde; mua lại phần lớn quyền sở hữu hai t&ograve;a nh&agrave; văn ph&ograve;ng ở Boston, Massachusetts, đ&acirc;y l&agrave; khoản đầu tư bất động sản đầu ti&ecirc;n của c&ocirc;ng ty tại Hoa Kỳ của c&ocirc;ng ty trong 20 năm.</p>\r\n<table class=\"MASTERCMS_TPL_TABLE\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-style: hidden; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3124_image003.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Dự &aacute;n nh&agrave; ở của Haseko Corporation</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Thị trường ch&acirc;u &Aacute; đang ph&aacute;t triển cũng l&agrave; một mục ti&ecirc;u đầy hứa hẹn cho c&aacute;c doanh nghiệp x&acirc;y dựng Nhật Bản. Tại Hải Ph&ograve;ng, Việt Nam, dự &aacute;n ph&aacute;t triển kh&aacute;ch sạn quy m&ocirc; lớn \"Dự &aacute;n Waterfront City\" đ&atilde; được ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 3 bởi Daiwa House Industry v&agrave; Fujita. Kh&aacute;ch sạn c&oacute; tổng diện t&iacute;ch 39.814m2 hướng đến kh&aacute;ch doanh nh&acirc;n Nhật Bản v&agrave; kh&aacute;ch du lịch trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nước.</p>\r\n<p>Kumagai Gumi v&agrave; Sumitomo Forestry đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh lập một li&ecirc;n doanh tại Singapore để th&uacute;c đẩy ph&aacute;t triển bất động sản ở nước ngo&agrave;i. Dự &aacute;n 50.000 m&eacute;t vu&ocirc;ng gồm một chung cư cao tầng v&agrave; một t&ograve;a nh&agrave; thương mại sẽ được ph&aacute;t triển ở Jakarta, Indonesia l&agrave; dự &aacute;n đầu ti&ecirc;n của c&ocirc;ng ty.</p>\r\n<p>Tập đo&agrave;n Toda đ&atilde; đặt Brazil l&agrave; một trong những mục ti&ecirc;u mới của m&igrave;nh. N&oacute; đ&atilde; khởi động một dự &aacute;n x&acirc;y dựng nh&agrave; m&aacute;y điện gi&oacute; ngo&agrave;i khơi ở v&ugrave;ng đ&ocirc;ng bắc của đất nước. Tổng sản lượng điện l&agrave; 27,7 MW v&agrave; dự kiến bắt đầu hoạt động v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 7 năm 2021. C&ocirc;ng ty hy vọng sẽ mở rộng sang lĩnh vực kinh doanh bất động sản trong tương lai. (2020/9/09)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>The Daily Engineering and Construction News of Japan</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"img-random\" class=\"category tin-cu-hon\">\r\n<div class=\"scroller-status\">\r\n<p class=\"infinite-scroll-error\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\"><strong>（建筑）-日本建筑承包商正在从事除建筑合同以外的海外业务。</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3123_image001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>户田风力发电公司</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>它包括房地产投资，大规模开发和可再生能源，旨在积累业务知识并使其产品组合多样化。 Haseko Corporation在8月宣布，它将参与美国郊区Los Angels的292套住房开发项目。工程将于2022年开始，并于2024年完工。高松建筑集团（Takamatsu Construction Group）的美国子公司已与一家当地房地产公司建立了一家合资企业，以开发位于许多豪华物业所在地的加利福尼亚度假区的公寓楼。</p>\r\n<p>户田公司购买了加利福尼亚州尔湾市的一栋办公楼，这是该国的第一笔全面房地产投资。Taisei Corporation获得了在马萨诸塞州波士顿拥有两座办公楼的多数权利，这是该公司20年来首次在美国进行房地产投资。</p>\r\n<table class=\"MASTERCMS_TPL_TABLE\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-style: hidden; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3124_image003.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">长谷子的住宅项目</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>不断增长的亚洲市场也是日本建筑业的有希望的目标。在越南海防，Daiwa House Industry和Fujita于3月完成了大型酒店开发项目&ldquo; Waterfront City Project&rdquo;。总面积为39,814平方米的酒店面向日本商务旅客以及国内外游客。</p>\r\n<p>熊谷龟尾和住友林业在新加坡成立了一家合资企业，以促进海外房地产开发。该公司的第一个项目是在印度尼西亚雅加达开发的占地50,000平方米的高层公寓和商业建筑项目。</p>\r\n<p>户田公司已将巴西定为其新目标之一。它启动了在该国东北部建设海上风力发电厂的项目。总发电量为27.7兆瓦，计划于2021年7月开始运行。该公司希望&ldquo;将来能够扩展到房地产业务&rdquo;。（2020/9/09）</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>日本的每日工程建设新闻</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"img-random\" class=\"category tin-cu-hon\">\r\n<div class=\"scroller-status\">\r\n<p class=\"infinite-scroll-error\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\"><strong><strong><span class=\"goog-text-highlight\">（建設）-日本の建設請負業者は、建設契約以外の海外事業に着手している</span></strong></strong>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3123_image001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"meta mb10 clearfix\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>戸田風力発電所&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"category article-content __MASTERCMS_CONTENT __MB_CONTENT_FOR_PRINTER\">\r\n<div id=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL_3\" class=\"__MB_MASTERCMS_EL item-content\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>不動産投資、大規模開発、再生可能エネルギーなど、ビジネスノウハウの蓄積とポートフォリオの多様化を目指しています。長谷工コーポレーションは8月、米国ロサンゼルス郊外での292戸の住宅開発プロジェクトに参加すると発表した。建設は2022年に始まり、2024年に完成する予定です。高松コンストラクショングループの米国子会社は、多くの高級物件が位置するカリフォルニアのリゾートエリアにアパートを開発するために地元の不動産会社との合弁会社を設立しました。</p>\r\n<p>戸田建設は、カリフォルニア州アーバインにあるオフィスビルを購入しました。これは、カリフォルニア州で最初の本格的な不動産投資です。大成建設は、マサチューセッツ州ボストンにある2つのオフィスビルの所有権の過半数を取得し、20年ぶりに米国の不動産投資を行いました。</p>\r\n<table class=\"MASTERCMS_TPL_TABLE\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-style: hidden; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3124_image003.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">ハセコによる住宅プロジェクト</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>成長するアジア市場は、日本の建設業にとっても有望なターゲットです。ベトナムのハイフォンでは、大和ハウス工業と藤田が3月に大規模ホテル開発「ウォーターフロントシティプロジェクト」を完了しました。総面積39,814平方メートルのホテルは、日本のビジネス旅行者と国内外の観光客を対象としています。</p>\r\n<p>熊谷組と住友林業は、海外の不動産開発を促進するためにシンガポールで合弁会社を立ち上げました。インドネシアのジャカルタで開発される高層マンションと商業ビルの50,000平方メートルのプロジェクトは、同社の最初のプロジェクトです。</p>\r\n<p>戸田建設は、ブラジルを新たなターゲットのひとつに掲げています。国の北東部に洋上風力発電所を建設するプロジェクトを開始しました。総出力は27.7MWで、2021年7月に運転を開始する予定です。同社は「将来的には不動産事業への拡大」を目指しています。（2020/9/09）</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span class=\"goog-text-highlight\">日刊建設工業新聞社</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"img-random\" class=\"category tin-cu-hon\">\r\n<div class=\"scroller-status\">\r\n<p class=\"infinite-scroll-error\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<p><strong>(</strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">건설</span></strong><strong>)-</strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">일본</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">건설업자가</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">건설</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">계약</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">이외의</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">해외</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">사업에</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">착수하고</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span lang=\"KO\">있습니다</span></strong><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"__img_mastercms\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Japanese construction companies looking for new opportunities of overseas investment, renewable energy\" src=\"https://baoxaydung.com.vn/stores/news_dataimages/thuylinh/092020/15/10/3123_image001.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0/\" /></strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">사업</span> <span lang=\"KO\">노하우</span> <span lang=\"KO\">축적과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">포트폴리오</span> <span lang=\"KO\">다각화를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">목표로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">부동산</span> <span lang=\"KO\">투자</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">대규모</span> <span lang=\"KO\">개발</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">신</span> <span lang=\"KO\">재생</span><strong> </strong><span lang=\"KO\">에너지</span> <span lang=\"KO\">등</span> (<span lang=\"KO\">주</span>)<span lang=\"KO\">하세코는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">지난</span> 