EN-US\">提升</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">了</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">公司</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">的</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">地位</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">。</span>Binh Duong Office<span lang=\"KO\">의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새로운</span> <span lang=\"KO\">단계를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">알리는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">중요한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">이정표입니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">회사의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">위상을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">먼</span> <span lang=\"KO\">길로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">발전시키고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">향상시키는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">글로벌</span>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'quang', 'Ngọc', 18, 'blog', '2020-12-14 03:24:48', '2022-05-17 11:51:13'),
(82, NULL, 'Minh Global celebrates the groundbreaking ceremony of Reclaimed Wood Furniture Factory project', 'Minh Global khởi công dự án Nhà Máy Gỗ Nội Thất Từ Gỗ Tái Chế', 'Minh Global庆祝再生木家具厂项目开工仪式举行', 'Minh Global、再生木材家具工場プロジェクトの起工式を開催', 'Minh Global, Reclaimed Wood Furniture Factory 프로젝트 착공식 축하', '', '', 'minh-global-khoi-cong-du-an-nha-may-go-noi-that-tu-go-tai-che', '1610549062title.jpg', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"0\">On January 7, 2021, Minh Global Corp. and the owner, PGT-Reclaimed Vietnam Co., Ltd. held the groundbreaking ceremony for the Reclaimed Wood Furniture Factory project at Lot N7,</span> <span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\">N8, N9, N10, N2 &amp; D3 roads, Nam Tan Uyen Industrial Park, Tan Uyen, Binh Duong province.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xG6Whgk/W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\">Reclaimed Wood Furniture Factory project has a total floor area of 72,722 m2, including items: carpentry and paint workshop, finished product warehouse, semi-finished warehouse, office, cafeteria, auxiliary houses and landscape infrastructure. Minh Global is the Design &amp; Build contractor of the project. Project expected completion time and handover to owner in August 2021.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8BZ1Xtz/W2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\">Pictures from groundbreaking ceremony:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6XK3KS8/W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/z6jdHG3/W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NjpJQ3g/W5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/L1FKFqx/W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x168LJW/W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1sXw7vn/W8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Dkqp5V0/W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LphxPJP/W10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng&agrave;y 07/01/2021, C&ocirc;ng ty Cổ Phần Đầu tư Ph&aacute;t triển Minh Global v&agrave; chủ đầu tư, c&ocirc;ng ty TNHH PGT-Reclaimed Việt Nam tổ chức lễ động thổ dự &aacute;n Nh&agrave; M&aacute;y Gỗ Nội Thất Từ Gỗ T&aacute;i Chế tại L&ocirc; N7, N8, N9, N10, đường N2 &amp; D3, Khu c&ocirc;ng nghiệp Nam T&acirc;n Uy&ecirc;n, T&acirc;n Uy&ecirc;n, tỉnh B&igrave;nh Dương</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xG6Whgk/W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dự &aacute;n Nh&agrave; M&aacute;y Gỗ Nội Thất Từ Gỗ T&aacute;i Chế c&oacute; tổng diện t&iacute;ch s&agrave;n 72.722 m<sup>2 </sup>, gồm c&aacute;c hạng mục: xưởng mộc v&agrave; sơn, nh&agrave; kho th&agrave;nh phẩm, nh&agrave; kho b&aacute;n th&agrave;nh phẩm, văn ph&ograve;ng, căn tin, c&aacute;c nh&agrave; phụ trợ v&agrave; hạ tầng cảnh quan. Minh Global l&agrave; đơn vị thầu ch&iacute;nh thiết kế &amp; thi c&ocirc;ng cho dự &aacute;n. Thời gian dự kiến ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh v&agrave; b&agrave;n giao cho CĐT v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 08/2021.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8BZ1Xtz/W2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Một số h&igrave;nh ảnh từ lễ động thổ:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6XK3KS8/W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/z6jdHG3/W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NjpJQ3g/W5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/L1FKFqx/W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x168LJW/W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1sXw7vn/W8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Dkqp5V0/W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LphxPJP/W10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2021年1月7日，Minh Global Corporation与业主PGT-Reclaimed Vietnam Co.Ltd 在平阳省南新渊工业区D3路N7、N8、N9、N10、N2地块举行了翻新木家具厂项目工程奠基仪式。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xG6Whgk/W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">翻新木家具厂项目总建筑面积约7.3万平方米，项目包括：木工及油漆车间、成品库、半成品库、办公室、食堂、辅助用房及景观基础设施。Minh Global是本项目的设计与施工承包商。项目预计竣工及移交给业主时间为2021年8月。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8BZ1Xtz/W2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">奠基仪式的图片:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6XK3KS8/W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/z6jdHG3/W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NjpJQ3g/W5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/L1FKFqx/W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x168LJW/W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1sXw7vn/W8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Dkqp5V0/W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LphxPJP/W10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2021年1月7日、Minh Global Corp.とオーナーのPGT-Reclaimed Vietnam Co, Ltd.は、ビンズン省タンウエン市ナムタンウエン工業団地Nam Tan Uyen工業団地N7,N8,N9,N10,N2,D3道路で再生木材家具工場プロジェクトの起工式を行った。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xG6Whgk/W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">再生木材家具工場プロジェクトの総床面積は72,722m2で、その中には大工・塗装工場、完成品倉庫、半完成品倉庫、オフィス、カフェテリア、補助住宅、景観インフラなどが含まれている。Minh Globalがプロジェクトの設計・施工を担当します。プロジェクトの完成時期は2021年8月を予定しており、オーナーへの引き渡しは2021年8月を予定しています。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8BZ1Xtz/W2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">起工式の写真:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6XK3KS8/W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/z6jdHG3/W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NjpJQ3g/W5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/L1FKFqx/W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x168LJW/W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1sXw7vn/W8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Dkqp5V0/W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LphxPJP/W10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>', '<div>\r\n<p>2021 <span lang=\"EN-US\">년</span> 1 <span lang=\"EN-US\">월</span> 7 <span lang=\"EN-US\">일</span>, Minh Global Corp.<span lang=\"EN-US\">과 소유주 인</span> PGT-Reclaimed Vietnam Co., Ltd.<span lang=\"EN-US\">는 남남의</span> Lot N7, N8, N9, N10, N2 &amp; D3 roads<span lang=\"EN-US\">에서</span> Reclaimed Wood Furniture Factory <span lang=\"EN-US\">프로젝트 착공식을 가졌습니다</span>. Binh Duong <span lang=\"EN-US\">지방</span> Tan Uyen, Tan Uyen <span lang=\"EN-US\">산업 단지</span>.</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xG6Whgk/W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">매립 목재 가구 공장 프로젝트는 목공 및 페인트 작업장</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">완제품 창고</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">반제품 창고</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">사무실</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">카페테리아</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">보조 주택 및 조경 인프라를 포함하여 총 바닥 면적이</span> 72,722m2<span lang=\"KO\">입니다</span>. Minh Global<span lang=\"KO\">은 프로젝트의 설계 및 빌드 계약자입니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">프로젝트 예상 완료 시간 및</span> 2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> 8 <span lang=\"KO\">월 소유자에게 양도</span>.</p>\r\n<p>기공식 사진 :</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8BZ1Xtz/W2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"auto\" data-phrase-index=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6XK3KS8/W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/z6jdHG3/W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/L1FKFqx/W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x168LJW/W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1sXw7vn/W8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Dkqp5V0/W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LphxPJP/W10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'quang', 'Ngọc', 18, 'blog', '2021-01-13 14:44:22', '2022-05-17 11:51:23'),
(84, NULL, 'Minh Global\'s 2020 Year-end party at Lan Rung resort', 'Buổi tiệc tất niên 2020 ấm áp của Minh Global tại Lan Rừng resort', 'Minh Global 在Lan Rung度假村举行的2020年年终尾牙晚宴', 'ランルンリゾートでのミングローバルの暖かい年末パーティー2020', '란룽 리조트 민 글로벌 2020 년 연말 파티', '', '', 'buoi-tiec-tat-nien-2020-am-ap-cua-minh-global-tai-lan-rung-resort', '16118239491.jpg', NULL, '<p>In two days 23 and 24 January 2021 Minh Global held a year-end party combining vacation for all staff members and their families. The vacation, called \"Family day\" held for 29 families, 98 attendees, including 31 children, spent a comfortable and meaningful weekend.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/11.jpg\" alt=\"Phần trao qu&agrave; cho c&aacute;c em nhỏ\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global\'s staff, under the guidance and direction of General Director Le Phuoc Binh, have raised to a new level to be ready to \"step into the big playing field\". The motto \"Always quest for Best\" with the meaning of constantly raising the level towards higher values has been spread to all the company team and spread to the community.</p>\r\n<p>Although the Spring gifts were small, they also stirred up people\'s hearts in the exciting lottery performance. A special award is a Microsoft Surface Pro computer awarded to Mr. Truong Huynh Anh Tran with a lucky and meaningful lottery number 01. He were the first to show up on this Gala Dinner.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>After all, family is what we look forward to. Small families in the Minh Global family have felt the joy, warmth, relaxation and intimacy in the company\'s \"Family Day\". Believing with the right motto and strong capacity, Minh Global will make a bold mark on its new year 2021.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"961\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143869652_201774734986820_8325793500387890986_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143509771_201774668320160_9180415547459983655_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143899797_201774631653497_8113467262583656487_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>MINH GLOBAL DEVELOPMENT see YOU in 2021!</strong></p>', '<p>Trong hai ng&agrave;y 23 v&agrave; 24 th&aacute;ng 1 năm 2021 Minh Global đ&atilde; tổ chức tiệc Tất ni&ecirc;n kết hợp kỳ nghỉ m&aacute;t cho to&agrave;n bộ c&aacute;n bộ nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n v&agrave; gia đ&igrave;nh của họ. Kỳ nghỉ m&aacute;t với t&ecirc;n gọi \"Family day\" đ&atilde; tổ chức cho 29 gia đ&igrave;nh, 98 người tham dự trong đ&oacute; c&oacute; 31 trẻ em trải qua một cuối tuần thật thoải m&aacute;i v&agrave; nhiều &yacute; nghĩa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/11.jpg\" alt=\"Phần trao qu&agrave; cho c&aacute;c em nhỏ\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Đội ngũ c&aacute;n bộ Minh Global dưới sự dẫn dắt v&agrave; định hướng của Tổng gi&aacute;m đốc L&ecirc; Phước B&igrave;nh đ&atilde; n&acirc;ng tầm l&ecirc;n một đẳng cấp mới để sẵn s&agrave;ng \"bước ra s&acirc;n chơi lớn\". Phương ch&acirc;m \"Always quest for Best\" với &yacute; nghĩa kh&ocirc;ng ngừng n&acirc;ng tầm để hướng đến gi&aacute; trị cao hơn đ&atilde; được lan tỏa đến tất cả đội ngũ c&ocirc;ng ty v&agrave; lan tỏa đến cộng động.</p>\r\n<p>Những m&oacute;n qu&agrave; Xu&acirc;n tuy nhỏ nhưng cũng l&agrave;m x&ocirc;n xao l&ograve;ng người trong tiết mục bốc thăm tr&uacute;ng thưởng đầy s&ocirc;i động. Giải thưởng đặc biệt l&agrave; 1 chiếc m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh Microsoft Surface Pro được trao cho anh Trương Huỳnh Anh Trấn với con số bốc thăm 01 đầy may mắn v&agrave; &yacute; nghĩa. Anh đ&atilde; l&agrave; người đầu ti&ecirc;n c&oacute; mặt trong đ&ecirc;m Gala Dinner n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Sau tất cả, gia đ&igrave;nh l&agrave; thứ ch&uacute;ng ta hướng về. C&aacute;c gia đ&igrave;nh nhỏ trong đại gia đ&igrave;nh Minh Global đ&atilde; cảm nhận niềm vui, sự ấm &aacute;p, thư gi&atilde;n v&agrave; th&acirc;n t&igrave;nh trong \"Ng&agrave;y gia đ&igrave;nh\" của c&ocirc;ng ty. Tin tưởng với phương ch&acirc;m đ&uacute;ng đắn v&agrave; thực lực vững mạnh, Minh Global sẽ đặt dấu ấn đậm n&eacute;t của m&igrave;nh trong năm mới 2021.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"961\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143869652_201774734986820_8325793500387890986_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143509771_201774668320160_9180415547459983655_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143899797_201774631653497_8113467262583656487_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>MINH GLOBAL DEVELOPMENT see YOU in 2021!</strong></p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2021年1月23日至24日两天，Minh Global举行了年终尾牙联欢晚会，为所有员工及其家人提供了假期。 这个假期称为&ldquo;家庭日&rdquo;，为29个家庭举行，有98名参加者，其中包括31名儿童，度过了一个舒适而有意义的周末。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/11.jpg\" alt=\"Phần trao qu&agrave; cho c&aacute;c em nhỏ\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global的员工在总经理Le Phuoc Binh的指导和指导下已提升到一个新的水平，准备&ldquo;步入广阔的竞争环境&rdquo;。 方针口号为``始终追求最佳\'\'，其含义是不断将水平提高到更高的价值，已传播到所有公司团队人员，同时也传播到社区。</p>\r\n<p>尽管春节礼物是不大的，但它们在令人兴奋的彩票表演中也引起了人们的热烈关注。 特别奖是授予Truong Huynh Anh Tran先生的Microsoft Surface Pro计算机，其幸运号和有意义的彩票号码为01。 他是第一个出现在此晚宴上的人。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>毕竟，家庭是我们的最终期待的。 在公司的&ldquo;家庭日&rdquo;中，Minh Global大家庭中的小家庭感到了喜悦，温暖，放松和亲密。 Minh Global秉承正确的方针和强大的能力，将在2021年新的一年中树立出破的烙印。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"961\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143869652_201774734986820_8325793500387890986_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143509771_201774668320160_9180415547459983655_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143899797_201774631653497_8113467262583656487_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>MINH GLOBAL DEVELOPMENT see YOU in 2021!</strong></p>', '<p>2021年1月23日と24日の2日間で、ミングローバルはすべてのスタッフとその家族のために休暇を組み合わせた忘年会を開催しました。 29家族を対象に開催された「家族の日」と呼ばれる休暇は、31人の子供を含む98人の参加者が快適で有意義な週末を過ごしました。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/11.jpg\" alt=\"Phần trao qu&agrave; cho c&aacute;c em nhỏ\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Minh Globalのスタッフは、Le Phuoc Binh事務局長の指導と指示の下、「大きな競争の場に足を踏み入れる」準備ができている新しいレベルに引き上げられました。 より高い価値に向けて常にレベルを上げることを意味する「常に最高を追求する」というモットーは、すべての企業チームに広まり、コミュニティに広まりました。</p>\r\n<p>春のプレゼントは少額でしたが、抽選会で人々の心を躍らせました。 特別賞は、幸運で意味のある宝くじ番号01でTruong Huynh AnhTran氏に授与されたMicrosoftSurfaceProコンピューターです。 あなたはこのガラディナーに最初に現れました。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>結局のところ、家族は私たちが楽しみにしているものです。 ミングローバルファミリーの小さな家族は、会社の「家族の日」で喜び、暖かさ、リラックス、そして親密さを感じました。 Minh Globalは、正しいモットーと強力な能力を信じて、2021年の新年に大胆な印を付けます。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"961\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143869652_201774734986820_8325793500387890986_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143509771_201774668320160_9180415547459983655_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143899797_201774631653497_8113467262583656487_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>MINH GLOBAL DEVELOPMENT see YOU in 2021!</strong></p>', '<p>2021 년 1 월 23 일과 24 일 이틀 동안 Minh Global은 모든 직원과 그 가족을 위해 휴가를 결합한 연말 파티를 열었습니다. \'가족의 날\'이라는 방학은 29 가정, 어린이 31 명을 포함 해 98 명이 참석 한 가운데 편안하고 의미 있는 주말을 보냈다.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/11.jpg\" alt=\"Phần trao qu&agrave; cho c&aacute;c em nhỏ\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global의 직원들은 Le Phuoc Binh 총감독의지도와 지시에 따라 \"큰 경쟁의 장에 발을 들여 놓을\"준비를 하기 위해 새로운 차원으로 올라갔습니다. 더 높은 가치를 향한 수준을 지속적으로 높이는 의미로 \"항상 최고를 향한 추구\"를 모토로 회사 전 팀에 전파하고 지역 사회에 전파하였습니다.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">봄</span> <span lang=\"KO\">선물은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">작았지만</span> <span lang=\"KO\">신나는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">복권</span> <span lang=\"KO\">공연으로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">사람들의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">마음을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">흔들기도 했다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">특별상은</span> Truong Huynh Anh Tran <span lang=\"KO\">씨에게</span> <span lang=\"KO\">행운과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">의미 있는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">복권</span> <span lang=\"KO\">번호</span> 01<span lang=\"KO\">을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">수여하는</span> Microsoft Surface Pro <span lang=\"KO\">컴퓨터입니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">그는 이</span> <span lang=\"KO\">갈라</span> <span lang=\"KO\">디너에</span> <span lang=\"KO\">처음으로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">등장했습니다</span>.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">결국</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가족은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">우리가</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기대하는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">것입니다</span>. Minh Global <span lang=\"KO\">가족의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">작은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가족들은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">회사의</span> \"Family Day\"<span lang=\"KO\">에서</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기쁨</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">따뜻함</span>, <span lang=\"KO\">휴식</span> <span lang=\"KO\">및</span> <span lang=\"KO\">친밀함을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">느꼈습니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">올바른</span> <span lang=\"KO\">모토와</span> <span lang=\"KO\">강력한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">역량으로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">민</span> <span lang=\"KO\">글로벌은</span> 2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새해를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">맞이할</span> <span lang=\"KO\">것입니다</span>.</p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143869652_201774734986820_8325793500387890986_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143509771_201774668320160_9180415547459983655_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../public/admin/images/143899797_201774631653497_8113467262583656487_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"719\" /></strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>MINH GLOBAL DEVELOPMENT<span lang=\"EN-US\">가</span> 2021<span lang=\"EN-US\">년에</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">만나요</span>!</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ngọc', 'Quốc', 18, 'blog', '2021-01-28 08:52:29', '2022-05-17 11:51:36');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`blog_id`, `blog_ten`, `blog_ten_en`, `blog_ten_vi`, `blog_ten_zh`, `blog_ten_ja`, `blog_ten_kr`, `blog_place`, `blog_place_en`, `blog_slug`, `blog_thumb`, `blog_noidung`, `blog_noidung_en`, `blog_noidung_vi`, `blog_noidung_zh`, `blog_noidung_ja`, `blog_noidung_kr`, `blog_noibat`, `blog_hienthi`, `blog_title`, `blog_mota`, `blog_mota_vi`, `blog_mota_en`, `blog_mota_zh`, `blog_mota_ja`, `blog_mota_kr`, `blog_keyword`, `blog_nguoiviet`, `blog_editor`, `blog_blogcatid`, `blog_type`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(85, NULL, 'Minh Global Development early spring 2021 meeting', 'Họp mặt đầu xuân 2021 của Minh Global Development', 'Minh Global Development 2021年初开春会面', '2021年春初頭のミングローバル開発会議', 'Minh Global Development 이른 봄 2021 회의', '', '', 'hop-mat-dau-xuan-2021-cua-minh-global-development', '1614077419z2344077002957_5a6b0a04a8b50fed7de23fb28e7981dd.jpg', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At 8:30 a.m on Saturday, February 20, 2021, MGD\'s General Director Mr. Le Phuoc Binh had a meeting and congratulated the company\'s new year 2021 to all officers and employees of the company. After sending the New Year\'s greetings, the New Year red envelopes were handed to the staff to deliver the message of a lucky new year and full of fortune.</p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077002957_5a6b0a04a8b50fed7de23fb28e7981dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global Development welcomes the new year 2021 with higher goals than the old year 2020. Mr. Le Phuoc Binh had a few messages at the beginning of the year with all staff, wishing each individual to bring out their great potential as possible and work harder together to fulfill the company\'s goal of joining a group of businesses with revenue of approximately VND 1,000 billion. All staff members receive the new task with a confident and ready attitude.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077437035_0ef369ab087e45e984be1aef4d56f99d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>At the same time, Minh Global Development also welcomed new employees to the MGD team, new experienced and enthusiastic elements will together contribute to building a stronger and more successful team. \"A strong team is built on strong individuals\". Minh Global Development collective welcomes the new year 2021.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>V&agrave;o l&uacute;c 8 giờ 30 ph&uacute;t s&aacute;ng thứ bảy ng&agrave;y 20/2/2021, Tổng gi&aacute;m đốc MGD anh L&ecirc; Phước B&igrave;nh đ&atilde; c&oacute; buổi gặp gỡ v&agrave; gửi lời Ch&uacute;c mừng T&acirc;n Ni&ecirc;n 2021 với to&agrave;n thể c&aacute;n bộ v&agrave; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ty. Sau khi gửi lời ch&uacute;c mừng năm mới, c&aacute;c bao l&igrave; x&igrave; Tết được trao tận tay đến c&aacute;n bộ nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n mang đến th&ocirc;ng điệp về một năm mới may mắn v&agrave; t&agrave;i lộc đầy tr&agrave;n.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077002957_5a6b0a04a8b50fed7de23fb28e7981dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global Development ch&agrave;o đ&oacute;n năm mới 2021 với những mục ti&ecirc;u cao hơn năm cũ 2020. Anh L&ecirc; Phước B&igrave;nh đ&atilde; c&oacute; đ&ocirc;i lời nhắn nhủ đầu năm với to&agrave;n thể c&aacute;n bộ nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n, mong muốn mỗi một c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ph&aacute;t huy hết khả năng lớn nhất c&oacute; thể v&agrave; nỗ lực hơn nữa c&ugrave;ng nhau ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh mục ti&ecirc;u của c&ocirc;ng ty l&agrave; gia nhập nh&oacute;m <strong>doanh nghiệp đạt doanh thu xấp xỉ 1000 tỷ đồng. </strong>To&agrave;n thể c&aacute;n bộ nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n đ&oacute;n nhận nhiệm vụ mới với t&acirc;m thế tự tin v&agrave; sẵn s&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077437035_0ef369ab087e45e984be1aef4d56f99d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>C&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c, Minh Global Development cũng đ&atilde; ch&agrave;o đ&oacute;n những c&aacute;n bộ nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n mới gia nhập v&agrave;o đội ngũ MGD, những nh&acirc;n tố mới đầy kinh nghiệm v&agrave; nhiệt huyết sẽ c&ugrave;ng nhau g&oacute;p sức để x&acirc;y dựng đội ngũ ng&agrave;y một vững mạnh v&agrave; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng tr&ecirc;n mọi phương diện. <strong>&ldquo;Một tập thể vững mạnh được x&acirc;y dựng tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c c&aacute; thể mạnh mẽ&rdquo;. </strong>Tập thể Minh Global Development ch&agrave;o đ&oacute;n năm mới 2021.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">MGD总经理Le Phuoc Binh先生于2021年2月20日星期六上午8:30开会，向公司所有管理人员和员工祝贺2021年新。在发送新年问候之后，新年红包赠送给每一位人员，以传递新年幸运和充满财富的信息。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077002957_5a6b0a04a8b50fed7de23fb28e7981dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>2021年Minh Global Development迎接了比2020年更高的目标。Le Phuoc Binh先生在年初开春会面时与全体员工共同表达了愿望，希望每个人都发挥自己的巨大潜力，并努力工作。共同努力实现公司的目标，即加入收入约为1万亿越南盾的企业集团。所有员工都以自信和准备就绪的态度接受新任务。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077437035_0ef369ab087e45e984be1aef4d56f99d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>同时，Minh Global Development也欢迎MGD团队的新员工，新的经验和热情的元素将以各种方式共同为建立强大而成功的团队做出贡献。 &ldquo;强大的团队是建立在强大的个人基础上&rdquo;。 Minh Global Development集体团队欢迎2021年新的一年。</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">2021年2月20日土曜日の午前8時30分、MGDのゼネラルディレクターであるLe Phuoc Binh氏が会議を開き、会社のすべての役員と従業員に会社の新年を祝いました。新年の挨拶を送った後、幸運と幸運に満ちた新年のメッセージを伝えるために、新年の赤い封筒がスタッフに手渡されました。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077002957_5a6b0a04a8b50fed7de23fb28e7981dd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Minh Global Developmentは、2020年よりも高い目標を掲げて2021年の新年を迎えます。LePhuocBinh氏は、年初にすべてのスタッフにいくつかのメッセージを送り、各個人が可能な限り大きな可能性を引き出して働くことを願っています。約1兆VNDの収益を持つ企業グループに参加するという会社の目標を達成するために一緒に取り組むことはより困難です。すべてのスタッフは、自信を持って準備ができた態度で新しいタスクを受け取ります。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../public/admin/images/z2344077437035_0ef369ab087e45e984be1aef4d56f99d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" /></p>\r\n<p>同時に、Minh Global DevelopmentはMGDチームに新しい従業員を迎えました。新しい経験豊富で熱心な要素が一緒になって、強力で成功するチームの構築に貢献します。 「強いチームは強い個人の上に成り立っています」。 Minh Global Development Collectiveは、2021年の新年を迎えます。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<div>\r\n<p>2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> 2 <span lang=\"KO\">월</span> 20 <span lang=\"KO\">일</span> <span lang=\"KO\">토요일</span> <span lang=\"KO\">오전</span> 8<span lang=\"KO\">시</span> 30 <span lang=\"KO\">분에</span> MGD<span lang=\"KO\">의</span> Le Phuoc Binh <span lang=\"KO\">총감독이</span> <span lang=\"KO\">회의를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">갖고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">회사의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">모든</span> <span lang=\"KO\">임원과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">직원들에게</span> <span lang=\"KO\">회사의</span> 2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새해를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">축하했습니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">새해</span> <span lang=\"KO\">인사를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">보낸</span> <span lang=\"KO\">후</span> <span lang=\"KO\">직원들에게</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새해</span> <span lang=\"KO\">복</span> <span lang=\"KO\">주머니를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">건네</span> <span lang=\"KO\">주면서</span><span lang=\"KO\">행운과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">행운의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">메시지를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">전했다</span>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Minh Global Development<span lang=\"KO\">는</span> 2020 <span lang=\"KO\">년보다</span> <span lang=\"KO\">더</span> <span lang=\"KO\">높은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">목표로</span> 2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새해를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">맞이합니다</span>. Le Phuoc Binh <span lang=\"KO\">씨는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">연초에</span><span lang=\"KO\">모든</span> <span lang=\"KO\">직원과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">함께</span> <span lang=\"KO\">몇</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가지</span> <span lang=\"KO\">메시지를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가졌으며</span> <span lang=\"KO\">각</span> <span lang=\"KO\">개인이</span> <span lang=\"KO\">가능한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">큰</span> <span lang=\"KO\">잠재력을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">발휘하고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">더</span> <span lang=\"KO\">열심히</span> <span lang=\"KO\">일하기를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">바랍니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">약</span> 1,000 <span lang=\"KO\">억</span> VND<span lang=\"KO\">의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">매출을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">올리는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기업</span> <span lang=\"KO\">그룹에</span> <span lang=\"KO\">합류한다는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">회사의</span> <span lang=\"KO\">목표를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">함께</span> <span lang=\"KO\">달성했습니다</span>. <span lang=\"KO\">모든</span> <span lang=\"KO\">직원은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">자신감</span> <span lang=\"KO\">있고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">준비된</span> <span lang=\"KO\">태도로</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새로운</span> <span lang=\"KO\">작업을 받습니다</span>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KO\">동시에</span> Minh Global Development<span lang=\"KO\">는</span> MGD <span lang=\"KO\">팀에</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새로운</span> <span lang=\"KO\">직원을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">환영했으며</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새로운</span> <span lang=\"KO\">경험과</span> <span lang=\"KO\">열정적</span> <span lang=\"KO\">인</span> <span lang=\"KO\">요소가</span> <span lang=\"KO\">함께</span><span lang=\"KO\">더</span> <span lang=\"KO\">강력하고</span> <span lang=\"KO\">성공적인</span> <span lang=\"KO\">팀을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">구축하는</span> <span lang=\"KO\">데</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기여할</span> <span lang=\"KO\">것입니다</span>. \"<span lang=\"KO\">강력한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">팀은</span> <span lang=\"KO\">강한</span> <span lang=\"KO\">개인을</span> <span lang=\"KO\">기반으로 합니다</span>.\" Minh Global Development <span lang=\"KO\">집단은</span> 2021 <span lang=\"KO\">년</span> <span lang=\"KO\">새해를</span> <span lang=\"KO\">맞이합니다</span>.</p>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ngọc', 'Ngọc', 18, 'blog', '2021-02-23 10:50:19', '2022-05-17 11:51:38'),
(86, NULL, 'Minh Global broke ground on the storage warehouse project of the Asia-Pacific pharmaceutical company', 'Minh Global động thổ dự án kho bảo quản của công ty dược phẩm Châu Á – Thái Bình Dương', 'Minh Global与亚太药品医疗公司存储仓库项目办理破土动工仪式', 'Minh Globalは、アジア太平洋の製薬会社のストレージウェアハウスプロジェクトに着手しました', '민 글로벌, 아시아 태평양 제약 회사 저장 창고 프로젝트 착공', '', '', 'minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong', '1621823826z2501605434144_4f3782164fdf7d3803f8897d3c5d3e98.jpg', NULL, '<p><a href=\"http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/\">http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/</a></p>\r\n<p>On May 20, at Dong Xoai 3 Industrial Park, Binh Phuoc Province, Minh Global Investment and Development Joint Stock Company held a groundbreaking ceremony for a warehouse project to store pharmaceuticals and medical supplies according to GSP standards. of Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Company</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186506328_5543421842397402_9025566329951028057_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=sXQg1RyyHyUAX-Xr-r-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=70aa9ef63fe931af9268a0d350d37e11&amp;oe=60CDFE78\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về đang đứng\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd, abbreviated APPC, was established on March 31, 2008 under business license number: 6000706406 is one of the distributors of infusion products in Vietnam. The company specializes in distributing products throughout Indochina and is aiming for the ASEAN community. The company\'s main field of activity is buying and selling Pharmaceuticals and medical equipment.</p>\r\n<p>About the general contractor: Minh Global Development Investment Joint Stock Company is a design, management and construction company with more than 10 years of experience in its field, Minh Global has completed many construction items such as Open Expansion of DIC Vietnam factory, Tai Ky food powder factory, etc., etc. In addition to the project of warehouse for storing pharmaceuticals and medical supplies according to GSP standards of Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Company, Recently, this contractor also won the bidding packages of many projects such as the furniture factory from recycled wood of PGT-RECLAIMED (VIETNAM) COMPANY LIMITED or the rice factory of CH LTD.</p>\r\n<p>Some pictures from the groundbreaking ceremony</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/189153683_5543422029064050_5317264191120017558_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=9fgqVEenCrsAX8qg-RM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=83b3dad82da08872a4dc1f3e4d5523ab&amp;oe=60CC36C8\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về ngo&agrave;i trời\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186508250_5543422209064032_2204824754536594894_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=cZedK1ycN4AAX_CKz1M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=7f9a81ac5fec937fa8e87ff9df758704&amp;oe=60CB1982\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về một hoặc nhiều người v&agrave; mọi người đang đứng\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Nguồn: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.vietnamconstruction.vn</span></p>', '<p><a href=\"http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/\">http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/\">http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>V&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 20 th&aacute;ng 05 vừa qua , tại Khu c&ocirc;ng nghiệp Đồng Xo&agrave;i 3 , Tỉnh B&igrave;nh Phước c&ocirc;ng ty CP đầu tư ph&aacute;t triển Minh Global đ&atilde; tổ chức lễ động thổ dự &aacute;n kho bảo quản dược phẩm , vật tư y tế theo ti&ecirc;u chuẩn GSP của C&ocirc;ng ty dược phẩm Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; &ndash; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh Dương&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186506328_5543421842397402_9025566329951028057_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=sXQg1RyyHyUAX-Xr-r-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=70aa9ef63fe931af9268a0d350d37e11&amp;oe=60CDFE78\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về đang đứng\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ty TNHH Dược phẩm Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; &ndash; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh Dương , viết tắt APPC, được th&agrave;nh lập ng&agrave;y 31 th&aacute;ng 03 năm 2008 theo giấy ph&eacute;p ĐKKD số: 6000706406 l&agrave; một trong những nh&agrave; ph&acirc;n phối c&aacute;c sản phẩm dịch truyền tại Việt Nam. C&ocirc;ng ty chuy&ecirc;n về&nbsp;ph&acirc;n phối sản phẩm tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n khu vực Đ&ocirc;ng Dương v&agrave; đang hướng đến cộng đồng chung ASEAN. Lĩnh vực hoạt động của c&ocirc;ng ty chủ yếu l&agrave; mua b&aacute;n Dược phẩm, trang thiết bị y tế.</p>\r\n<p>Về tổng thầu : C&ocirc;ng ty CP đầu tư ph&aacute;t triển Minh Global l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ty&nbsp; thiết kế , quản l&yacute; v&agrave; thi c&ocirc;ng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh với hơn 10 năm kinh nghiệm trong lĩnh vực của m&igrave;nh th&igrave; Minh Global đ&atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh nhiều hạng mục c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh như&nbsp;Mở rộng nh&agrave; m&aacute;y DIC Việt Nam,&nbsp;Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y bột thực phẩm t&agrave;i k&yacute; ,&hellip;vv..v&hellip;Ngo&agrave;i dự &aacute;n kho bảo quản dược phẩm , vật tư y tế theo ti&ecirc;u chuẩn GSP của C&ocirc;ng ty dược phẩm Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; &ndash; Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh Dương th&igrave; vừa qua nh&agrave; thầu n&agrave;y c&ograve;n tr&uacute;ng c&aacute;c g&oacute;i thầu của nhiều dự &aacute;n như&nbsp;Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y sản xuất đồ gỗ nội thất từ gỗ t&aacute;i chế của c&ocirc;ng ty&nbsp;PGT-RECLAIMED (VIETNAM) COMPANY LIMITED&nbsp; hay Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y l&uacute;a gạo của c&ocirc;ng ty&nbsp;CH LTD.</p>\r\n<p>Một số h&igrave;nh ảnh trong buổi lễ động thổ</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/189153683_5543422029064050_5317264191120017558_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=9fgqVEenCrsAX8qg-RM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=83b3dad82da08872a4dc1f3e4d5523ab&amp;oe=60CC36C8\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về ngo&agrave;i trời\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186508250_5543422209064032_2204824754536594894_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=cZedK1ycN4AAX_CKz1M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=7f9a81ac5fec937fa8e87ff9df758704&amp;oe=60CB1982\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về một hoặc nhiều người v&agrave; mọi người đang đứng\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Nguồn: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.vietnamconstruction.vn</span></p>', '<p><a href=\"http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/\">http://vietnamconstruction.vn/vi/minh-global-dong-tho-du-an-kho-bao-quan-cua-cong-ty-duoc-pham-chau-a-thai-binh-duong/</a></p>\r\n<p>On May 20, at Dong Xoai 3 Industrial Park, Binh Phuoc Province, Minh Global Investment and Development Joint Stock Company held a groundbreaking ceremony for a warehouse project to store pharmaceuticals and medical supplies according to GSP standards. of Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Company</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186506328_5543421842397402_9025566329951028057_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=sXQg1RyyHyUAX-Xr-r-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=70aa9ef63fe931af9268a0d350d37e11&amp;oe=60CDFE78\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về đang đứng\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd, abbreviated APPC, was established on March 31, 2008 under business license number: 6000706406 is one of the distributors of infusion products in Vietnam. The company specializes in distributing products throughout Indochina and is aiming for the ASEAN community. The company\'s main field of activity is buying and selling Pharmaceuticals and medical equipment.</p>\r\n<p>About the general contractor: Minh Global Development Investment Joint Stock Company is a design, management and construction company with more than 10 years of experience in its field, Minh Global has completed many construction items such as Open Expansion of DIC Vietnam factory, Tai Ky food powder factory, etc., etc. In addition to the project of warehouse for storing pharmaceuticals and medical supplies according to GSP standards of Asia-Pacific Pharmaceutical Company, Recently, this contractor also won the bidding packages of many projects such as the furniture factory from recycled wood of PGT-RECLAIMED (VIETNAM) COMPANY LIMITED or the rice factory of CH LTD.</p>\r\n<p>Some pictures from the groundbreaking ceremony</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent.fhan4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/189153683_5543422029064050_5317264191120017558_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=9fgqVEenCrsAX8qg-RM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan4-1.fna&amp;oh=83b3dad82da08872a4dc1f3e4d5523ab&amp;oe=60CC36C8\" alt=\"C&oacute; thể l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh về ngo&agrave;i trời\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/186508250_5543422209064032_2204824754536594894_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=b